== Notes ==
# The head of Thammasat University was originally called &quot;chancellor&quot; (ผู้ประศาสน์การ &quot;phu prasat kan&quot;). In 1952, the post was renamed &quot;rector&quot; (อธิการบดี &quot;athikanbodi&quot;) by then prime minister, Field Marshal Plaek Phibunsongkram, who also became the first rector of the university.

